# b1_dense.shot — every-tick screenshot through a normal platform fall.
# If the legs bounce in-and-out of the ground at 1-tick frequency, we'll
# catch it here. If they settle stable, the user's report points elsewhere.

window 1280 720
seed   1 1
out    build/shots/b1
mouse  900 360
contact_sheet sheet cols 8 cell 256 144

at  20 shot pre_t020
at  30 press right

# Walk off the spawn platform; landing should happen around tick 80-95.
burst land from 80 to 130 every 1
burst settled from 140 to 200 every 5

at 220 end
